import React from 'react'
import { FooterCont, FooterCreditsTitle, FooterLogo, FooterCreditsCont, FooterCreditsTextCont, FooterCreditsText, FooterCreditsTitle2, FooterCreditsInpCont, FooterCreditsInp, FooterCreditsBtn, FooterCreditsText2, FooterCreditsBtnsMainCont, FooterCreditsTextdesc, FooterCreditsBtnsCont, FooterCreditsBtnCont, FooterCreditsBtnGP, FooterCreditsBtnAS, FooterCreditsIconsCont, FooterCreditsIcon, CopyRights } from './style'
import { ReactComponent as QrCode } from '../../assets/Qr Code.svg'
import { ReactComponent as FacebookIcon } from '../../assets/Icon-Facebook.svg'
import { ReactComponent as TwitterIcon } from '../../assets/Icon-Twitter.svg'
import { ReactComponent as InstagramIcon } from '../../assets/icon-instagram.svg'
import { ReactComponent as LinkedInIcon } from '../../assets/Icon-Linkedin.svg'
import { ReactComponent as CopyIcon } from '../../assets/Copy.svg'

export default function Footer() {
    return (
        <FooterCont>
            <FooterCreditsCont>
                <FooterCreditsTextCont>
                    <FooterLogo>
                        Exclusive
                    </FooterLogo>
                    <FooterCreditsTitle2>
                        Subscribe
                    </FooterCreditsTitle2>
                    <FooterCreditsText>
                        Get 10% off your first order
                    </FooterCreditsText>
                    <FooterCreditsInpCont>
                        <FooterCreditsInp type='email' placeholder='Enter your email' />
                        <FooterCreditsBtn />
                    </FooterCreditsInpCont>
                </FooterCreditsTextCont>
                <FooterCreditsTextCont>
                    <FooterCreditsTitle>
                        Support
                    </FooterCreditsTitle>
                    <FooterCreditsText2>
                        111 Bijoy sarani, Dhaka,  DH 1515, Bangladesh.
                    </FooterCreditsText2>
                    <FooterCreditsText>
                        exclusive@gmail.com
                    </FooterCreditsText>
                    <FooterCreditsText>
                        +88015-88888-9999
                    </FooterCreditsText>
                </FooterCreditsTextCont>
                <FooterCreditsTextCont>
                    <FooterCreditsTitle>
                        Account
                    </FooterCreditsTitle>
                    <FooterCreditsText>
                        My Account
                    </FooterCreditsText>
                    <FooterCreditsText>
                        Login / Register
                    </FooterCreditsText>
                    <FooterCreditsText>
                        Cart
                    </FooterCreditsText>
                    <FooterCreditsText>
                        Wishlist
                    </FooterCreditsText>
                    <FooterCreditsText>
                        Shop
                    </FooterCreditsText>
                </FooterCreditsTextCont>
                <FooterCreditsTextCont>
                    <FooterCreditsTitle>
                        Quick Link
                    </FooterCreditsTitle>
                    <FooterCreditsText>
                        Privacy Policy
                    </FooterCreditsText>
                    <FooterCreditsText>
                        Terms Of Use
                    </FooterCreditsText>
                    <FooterCreditsText>
                        FAQ
                    </FooterCreditsText>
                    <FooterCreditsText>
                        Contact
                    </FooterCreditsText>
                </FooterCreditsTextCont>
                <FooterCreditsTextCont>
                    <FooterCreditsTitle>
                        Download App
                    </FooterCreditsTitle>
                    <FooterCreditsBtnsMainCont>
                        <FooterCreditsTextdesc>
                            Save $3 with App New User Only
                        </FooterCreditsTextdesc>
                        <FooterCreditsBtnsCont>
                            <QrCode />
                            <FooterCreditsBtnCont>
                                <FooterCreditsBtnGP href='#' />
                                <FooterCreditsBtnAS href='#' />
                            </FooterCreditsBtnCont>
                        </FooterCreditsBtnsCont>
                    </FooterCreditsBtnsMainCont>
                    <FooterCreditsIconsCont>
                        <FooterCreditsIcon href='#'>
                            <FacebookIcon />
                        </FooterCreditsIcon>
                        <FooterCreditsIcon href='#'>
                            <TwitterIcon />
                        </FooterCreditsIcon>
                        <FooterCreditsIcon href='#'>
                            <InstagramIcon />
                        </FooterCreditsIcon>
                        <FooterCreditsIcon href='#'>
                            <LinkedInIcon />
                        </FooterCreditsIcon>
                    </FooterCreditsIconsCont>
                </FooterCreditsTextCont>
            </FooterCreditsCont>
            <CopyRights>
                <CopyIcon />
                Copyright Rimel 2022. All right reserved
            </CopyRights>
        </FooterCont>
    )
}
